// ["Glm4ForCausalLM"], the THUDM/GLM-4-9B-0414 / zai-org/GLM-4 text family):
// tests/fixtures/tiny_glm4.* is a pico randomly-initialized HF
// Glm4ForCausalLM (2 layers, 2 query heads sharing 1 kv head x 4 dims - GQA,
